🌅✨ “Golden hour magic from above.”
Lila, 25, stands on a cliff overlooking the Lofoten mountains and pristine beach, crop top and denim shorts catching the soft sunlight. Camera in hand, she captures every moment while her friend Marco enjoys the view nearby, and her little dog points curiously toward the sea. Cinematic vibes, warm tones, pure adventure. 📸🐾
